title: Unemployment rate in Jamaica 2019
summary: Overall Unemployment rate has increased over the Year.
Unemployment rate is roughly constant from 2010 to 2011, and finally slightly increasing from 2011 to 2012.
The steepest increase occurs in between the Year 2011 and 2012.
Maximum Unemployment rate, about 13.93 was reported at Year 2012
Minimum Unemployment rate about 12.37 was reached at Year 2010
